text:
I hit the wall today.  I had nothing left.

And then I got news that @WDGPublicHealth opened up #COVID19 #vaccine pre-registration to Phase 2 groups, including teachers & ed workers.

Tears of exhaustion, tears of relief, tears of hope for a better tomorrow.
